node.text:
We’ve all played Monopoly & know how to win the game.  The person with the most properties & rentals collects the most money & eventually dominates all their competition!⁣
⁣
The problem is it cost a lot of money in real life to afford rentals properties!⁣
⁣
𝘖𝘳 𝘥𝘰𝘦𝘴 𝘪𝘵?⁣
⁣
What if I told you I discovered a way to get sellers to give you their 𝗵𝗼𝘂𝘀𝗲𝘀 𝗳𝗼𝗿 𝗳𝗿𝗲𝗲!!!⁣
⁣
Seriously…. Like literally they just hand them to you and you can rent them out for cash flow and wealth building.⁣
⁣
I put together a special free report that I want to give to you since you follow me here on Instagram.⁣
⁣
DM me the word 𝗖𝗔𝗦𝗛𝗙𝗟𝗢𝗪 and I’ll send you a step-by-step free report plus give you access to a short training video that will show you everything you need to know in order to get free houses.⁣
⁣
I hope it helps,⁣
⁣
Cody Sperber aka The Clever Investor⁣
⁣

node.text: Hi haters 👋

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by 𝗖𝗼𝗱𝘆 𝗦𝗽𝗲𝗿𝗯𝗲𝗿 | 𝗥.𝗘. 𝗜𝗻𝘃𝗲𝘀𝘁𝗼𝗿 on September 13, 2021 tagging @cleverinvestor, @mannykhoshbin, @danfleyshman, @aaronwags, and @colehatter. May be an image of 5 people and people sitting.

node.text:
There are levels to this game.⁣
⁣
There is a price that needs to be paid to be at this level.⁣
⁣
There are gatekeepers and obstacles designed to keep you out.⁣
⁣
The system is not designed for you to win.⁣
⁣
Yet 1% of you will make it to the top.⁣
⁣
- You will break through.⁣
- You will overcome the pitfalls and become stronger.⁣
- You will get back up after being knocked down.⁣
- You will dominate your goals and destroy your enemies.⁣
⁣
1% of you will know what it feels like to be on this stage.⁣
⁣
And the best part is you know who you are.  You can feel it.  Deep inside.  That burning desire to win.  That ambition is so strong you can't sleep.  Can't think about anything else.⁣
⁣
It never leaves...never goes away.⁣
⁣
𝗝𝘂𝘀𝘁 𝗽𝘂𝗿𝗲 𝗲𝗻𝗲𝗿𝗴𝘆 𝗱𝗿𝗶𝘃𝗶𝗻𝗴 𝘆𝗼𝘂 𝗳𝗼𝗿𝘄𝗮𝗿𝗱.⁣
⁣
And I can't wait to meet you someday.  Become your peer.  Your friend.  And hopefully learn from you.⁣
⁣
Just think how great it's going to feel when you wake up and look around knowing that you did the "impossible".⁣
⁣
Never settle until that moment happens.⁣
⁣
𝙔𝙤𝙪 𝙜𝙤𝙩 𝙩𝙝𝙞𝙨!⁣
⁣
C Sperbs 😘⁣
⁣
⁣
⁣
⁣
#codysperber #cleverinvestor #success

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by 𝗖𝗼𝗱𝘆 𝗦𝗽𝗲𝗿𝗯𝗲𝗿 | 𝗥.𝗘. 𝗜𝗻𝘃𝗲𝘀𝘁𝗼𝗿 on September 13, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and sunglasses.

node.text:
🔥 𝗦𝗠𝗔𝗦𝗛 𝗟𝗜𝗞𝗘 & 𝗗𝗥𝗢𝗣 𝗔 𝗖𝗢𝗠𝗠𝗘𝗡𝗧 𝗜𝗙 𝗬𝗢𝗨 𝗔𝗚𝗥𝗘𝗘⁣
⁣
Every day we have to make a choice.⁣
⁣
You can use your past...⁣
⁣
the memories of those we lost⁣
the love we once felt⁣
the heartbreak⁣
the challenges⁣
the neglect⁣
the injustice⁣
and the pain⁣
⁣
to hold you back.  To 𝙡𝙞𝙢𝙞𝙩 your thoughts and paralyze you from moving forward.⁣
⁣
Or...⁣
⁣
you can use it to 𝙢𝙤𝙩𝙞𝙫𝙖𝙩𝙚 you to become the person you know you need to become based on the lessons life has given to you.⁣
⁣
Every day YOU get to choose how you react.⁣
⁣
Does life happen to you...for you...with you...or does life just happen?⁣
⁣
Depending on how you answer will tell me a lot about your 𝘦𝘮𝘰𝘵𝘪𝘰𝘯𝘢𝘭 𝘪𝘯𝘵𝘦𝘭𝘭𝘪𝘨𝘦𝘯𝘤𝘦!⁣
⁣
You see…all of my successful friends…ALL OF THEM…choose to be optimistic.  They choose to be positive (𝘦𝘷𝘦𝘯 𝘸𝘩𝘦𝘯 𝘵𝘩𝘦𝘪𝘳 𝘣𝘢𝘤𝘬𝘴 𝘢𝘨𝘢𝘪𝘯𝘴𝘵 𝘵𝘩𝘦 𝘸𝘢𝘭𝘭). They choose to use their pain as motivation to dominate their goals & create a better future for themselves & their families.⁣
⁣
It’s a choice.  Actually…it’s an OBLIGATION.⁣
⁣
They believe it’s their duty to take 𝗲𝘅𝘁𝗿𝗲𝗺𝗲 𝗼𝘄𝗻𝗲𝗿𝘀𝗵𝗶𝗽 & learn from their mistakes.⁣
⁣
No excuses.⁣
No blaming others.⁣
No being a victim.⁣
⁣
Just them accepting their situation & their environment as life happening for them & converting that energy into motivation to power forward.⁣
⁣
Today is a new day!⁣
⁣
𝗛𝗼𝘄 𝘄𝗶𝗹𝗹 𝘆𝗼𝘂 𝗰𝗵𝗼𝗼𝘀𝗲 𝘁𝗼 𝗼𝗽𝗲𝗿𝗮𝘁𝗲 𝘁𝗼𝗱𝗮𝘆?⁣
⁣
For those who took the time to read this...this message was meant for you 😘⁣
⁣
You're welcome,⁣
⁣
C.S.⁣
⁣
⁣
⁣
⁣
#codysperber #cleverinvestor #motivation #mindset #wealth

Meet Lyle (guy on the right in the first pic). My first #realestate mentor.  He taught me many lessons but the biggest one is the understanding that I’m not where I am in life because “I’m so great”… It’s because great people who have paved the path before me have locked arms with me to help me unlock my full #potential and become the person I always knew I could be.⁣
⁣
Remember that the next time you’re starting to have a little success and you feel your ego taking over.⁣
⁣
Smash like if you can see the value in having #mentors in your life!⁣
⁣
#success #realestateinvesting #codysperber #cleverinvestor
